# Disable USB autosuspend for Siliconworks touchscreen
# Prevents touchscreen from stopping after ~20 minutes of operation
#
# Issue: Touchscreen works after boot but stops responding after ~20 minutes
# Cause: USB autosuspend suspends the device after inactivity timeout
# Solution: Force power/control to "on" (never suspend)
#
# Device: Siliconworks SiW HID Touch Controller
# USB ID: 29bd:9302
ACTION=="add", SUBSYSTEM=="usb", ATTR{idVendor}=="29bd", ATTR{idProduct}=="9302", ATTR{power/control}="on"
